<table border="0" height="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="1007" style="background:url(images/bg1.jpg)" align="center">
<!-- fwtable fwsrc="未命名" fwbase="sr.jpg" fwstyle="Dreamweaver" fwdocid = "1344182167" fwnested="1" -->
  <tr><!-- row 1 -->
    <td align="right" valign="top">
    
		<!--标题开始-->
	      <div style="font-family:'华文行楷'; font-size:18pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center; padding-top:15px;">
	      	王常月的修道思想略述（二）
	      </div>
	      <!-- 副标题 -->
	      <div style="font-family:'华文行楷'; font-size:16pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center; padding-top:15px;">
	      	
	      </div>
	      <!--标题结束-->
		<div style="text-align:center"><a name="1" id="1"></a>
		<img name="sr_r3_c1" src="images/sr_r3_c1.gif" width="293" height="32" border="0" id="sr_r3_c1" alt="" /></div>
		<!--图片-->
		
		<!--图片结束-->
		<!-- 作者 -->
		
			<div style="font-family:'宋体'; font-size:12pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center;padding-bottom:8px;">
		      	
		    </div>
		
	   <div style="text-align:left; color:#88510c; font-size:14px; line-height:20px; width:900px; height:auto; margin:0 auto;">
	   		<!-- 显示内容 -->
	   		<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">五、忍辱降嗔火</span><span>73</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">王常月认为，&ldquo;修行人第一大病，是嗔毒。这嗔字，不是着了我相，就是着了人相，把六欲七情，都包在这嗔字里，千愆万过，都从嗔起&rdquo;。</span><span>74</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">王常月描述说，嗔毒未去之人，耳听他人骂我，目见他人侮我，便口出嗔言，火从心起，气由胆生。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">修行人不能降伏嗔心，根源在于不能忍辱。&ldquo;不能忍辱的人，其心不曾降伏，就如毒龙猛虎一般，只知辱他人，不容辱自己。&rdquo;</span><span>75</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">王常月指出，&ldquo;你既不肯忍人之辱，谁肯忍你之辱？你既不肯，他人又不肯，岂不生生相报，劫劫相争，屡世含冤，多身受苦，无有了期&rdquo;。</span><span>76</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">王常月认为，若能认识到因果报应之理，&ldquo;惟宜回想，我今受他欺者，毕竟我曾欺人，受他困者，我曾困他。遭刑遭难，遭害遇灾，悉因前生，自作自受&rdquo;。于是&ldquo;一切能忍，一切能受，不为荣而生喜心，不为辱而生嗔心&rdquo;，这样，&ldquo;从前恶孽，随心消散。自然六欲不生，三毒消灭，身心轻健，情性安和，苦恼痊平，冤仇和解&rdquo;。</span><span>77</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">可见，忍辱的目的是为了解冤释怨，消除夙业。&ldquo;无始以前，至于今日，凡有冤债，只愿偿还，损己利他，方为解脱。永归清净，不生不灭，圆满报身。不然前劫之债负不肯还他，今生之耻辱不肯让他，来世之报复自然不肯放你了也。此身如何得度，此心如何得空，此道如何得修？&rdquo;</span><span>78</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">王常月还把忍辱与内丹修炼联系起来，认为&ldquo;忍则无明火灭，自然五脏清净。忍则华池水生，自然六腑调泰。&hellip;&hellip;忍辱则肺液不枯，化作瑶池甘露。忍辱则肾精不耗，化变气海灵泉。忍辱则脾土不燥，化作五行正气，戊己刀圭自产&rdquo;。</span><span>79</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">按照王常月的描述，忍辱的道教神学意义是：&ldquo;忍辱则心平气和，肝火不生，化作青华救苦。忍辱则心神慈善，化作南斗消灾。&hellip;&hellip;忍辱则法身不漏，化作庄严妙相，光明正大现前。&rdquo;忍辱的社会意义是：&ldquo;能忍于国者，必有益于朝廷。能忍于家者，必有益于骨肉。&rdquo;对个人来说：&ldquo;能忍于身者，必有益于精神。能忍于心者，必有益于性命。&rdquo;总之，&ldquo;能忍则能受益&rdquo;。</span><span>80</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">六、偿夙业，报四恩</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">王常月认为，修行之人若要出轮回，必须把多劫以来积下的沉冤夙业偿还干净。对于以往的罪业，只能安心承受其报应，而不能寄望于消除。因为因果不昧，即使是大修行人，沉冤夙业也是逃不过的。《龙门心法》中说：&ldquo;上乘大器，凡心顿灭，则天地皆空，幻相成灰，则虚空一体，独有沉冤夙业，不能逃脱。所以如来佛祖，还偿夙业，丝毫不挂，方证释迦牟尼。六祖大师，洗净沉冤，细微承受，方证西天大鉴。&rdquo;</span><span>81</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">王常月认为，修行人若有逃脱沉冤夙业之心，根源还是在于不能把色身看破。《龙门心法》说：&ldquo;不肯酬还冤业，只愿逃脱者，只因把色身认真了，惟恐怕受苦报，打了他杀了他。&rdquo;而&ldquo;这一点不肯受苦的心，就是穷根，这一点不肯偿还之念，即下乘了&rdquo;。其结果就是，&ldquo;冤不肯彻底清澄，则冤根不断，后劫复生；业不肯还偿报复，则业因尚在，他生又遇&rdquo;。</span><span>82</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">因此，真正的大修行人，就应该立大志，&ldquo;忍一切辱，受一切苦&rdquo;，&ldquo;一心发愿，有冤者刀斧不避，照旧报酬；有业者水火不辞，照劫偿还。将这色身，视为外物；那法身清清静静，赤赤条条，无碍无遮，圆陀陀，光灼灼，去来自在。有福不愿受福，有苦不辞受苦了&rdquo;。</span><span>83</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">修行人不光要偿还夙业，还要报答四恩，否则果位不能圆满。王常月说：&ldquo;天地盖载，日月照临，皇王水土，父母养育，为之四恩。若不答报洪恩，难逃灾苦。灾不消，则福不长；福不长，则慧不绵；慧不绵，则性天不能常清静了也。&rdquo;</span><span>84</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">王常月认为，报恩不必拘于具体的行为，关键是心性功夫。&ldquo;心若有一毫障碍，见不得三清天尊、玉帝，如何唤得报天？一件事不能忍，一个人容不得，些儿肚量，狭窄心肠，惯发无明，常分人我，唤作甚么报地？必要我之身心，光明正大，才是报天地。&rdquo;&ldquo;你报天地之恩，须要明天地之道，开天地之心。只要自己无欺，一切私情都扫绝，自家心性放光明，藏污忍辱，能容物不自居，功效地灵，方是报天恩地德呢。至于我的工夫切笃，智慧发生，照见山河大地，万物人情无有隔碍，方是报日月呢。&rdquo;</span><span>85</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">王常月将忠孝的践履也归结到心性修持上。他说：&ldquo;至于我心绝妄存真，道高德重，神钦鬼服，上可感通帝座，下可役使雷霆，旱则祷雨润苍生，涝则求晴消水厄，福德可消兵火，正道可伏妖邪。上保皇图永固，上祝圣寿无疆，天下太平，万民安乐，方是报皇王呢。若是混混的，随波逐浪，念经礼忏，不修道德，不依戒律，不行好事，不积功行，临坛则鬼神不降，符法难行；遇劫则逃避深山，贪生怕死，如何报得皇王？&rdquo;</span><span>86</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">报父母之恩，也在于心性。王常月认为，&ldquo;心孝不为而孝&rdquo;，心存孝念，即使没有做什么，也已经是在尽孝道了。最大的孝，就是度祖先升天得道。而心性修持就有这个功效：&ldquo;心性光明，则祖宗得度，七玄上举，三代高冲，便是报父母。&rdquo;</span><span>87</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">王常月指出，要报四恩，须修心性。&ldquo;先灭三毒，贪嗔痴除净，则身心意三业净。三业净，则三灾八难，九横五苦，悉皆随心消灭，方能上报四恩也。&rdquo;&ldquo;四恩报尽，五福自增，生死两途，轮回可息。&rdquo;</span><span>88</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">七、只依着三教圣人正大光明的路走</span><span>89</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">全真道创教之始，即以融合三教为显著特色。王重阳说：&ldquo;儒门释户道相通，三教从来一祖风。&rdquo;</span><span>90</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&ldquo;心中端的莫生邪，三教搜来做一家。&rdquo;</span><span>91</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&ldquo;悟理莫忘三教语，全真修取四时春。&rdquo;</span><span>92</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">他在山东半岛创立的&ldquo;五会&rdquo;，都贯以&ldquo;三教&rdquo;名称。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">王常月继承了全真道融合三教的传统。他给自己的定位就是&ldquo;只依着三教圣人正大光明的路走&rdquo;。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">虽然王常月说自己&ldquo;既不通儒，又不通释&rdquo;，</span><span>93</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">但这不过是谦虚之言。《龙门心法》中随处可见引用儒、释经典之处。如在论述&ldquo;保命&rdquo;乃是&ldquo;保守上天所以赋畀之命&rdquo;时，就引用了儒家经典《中庸》&ldquo;天命之谓性&rdquo;和&ldquo;居易以俟命&rdquo;、《孟子》&ldquo;夭寿不二，修身以俟之&rdquo;、佛教《金刚经》&ldquo;云何得长寿，金刚不坏身&rdquo;等语句加以说明。</span><span>94</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">像这样引三教经典以说明其观点的做法，在《龙门心法》中时有所见。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">王常月在论述修心之法时，常常引用儒家的慎独、存诚、主敬之说。如说：&ldquo;心无二念意无他，慎独存诚归一愿。&rdquo;</span><span>95</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&ldquo;凡生心动念之顷，就要存诚主敬，暗自端详，细细行持。&rdquo;</span><span>96</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">王常月对佛教思想的吸收，突出表现在以戒定慧三学作为修行的根本上。他把初真、中极、天仙三坛大戒，即分别对应于戒、定、慧三学，认为&ldquo;若有能依戒定慧法门，行持信心，不生疑惑者，当知此人，决定成道&rdquo;，</span><span>97</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">并断定&ldquo;除此戒定慧之外，就别无甚么法子了&rdquo;。</span><span>98</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">道教有一部著名的经典《玉枢宝经》，其中有一段话是：&ldquo;入道者知止，守道者知谨，用道者知微。&rdquo;王常月解释说：&ldquo;入道者知止，即是持戒止念的功夫；守道者知谨，即是慎独精进的功夫；用道者知微，即是绝圣去智的功夫。&rdquo;</span><span>99</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">这里，持戒止念是佛教的思想，慎独是儒家的思想，而绝圣去智则是《道德经》的观点。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">王常月在论述出世&ldquo;须要看破天地万物皆是无常，世法人情皆成假幻&rdquo;时，说能看破这一切的，便是人的&ldquo;一点真灵&rdquo;。那么，什么是&ldquo;真灵&rdquo;呢？他也是用三教术语来解释：&ldquo;这点真灵，非同小可。在释谓之妙明真性，在儒谓之明德，在道谓之元神，又谓之祖气。那许多别名，说不可尽。&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">100</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">他又说，这&ldquo;一点真灵&rdquo;，也就是&ldquo;一点虚灵不昧之理性&rdquo;，儒家称为良知，释门唤作善知识，道门称为婴儿、元神。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">101</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">总之，在《龙门心法》中，三教的观点是融合在一起的，已经很难把它们一一区分开来了。王常月常常是三教并提，如说：&ldquo;三教祖师，有普度之慈心&rdquo;；</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">102</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&ldquo;将那个三教圣人，说不完的淡话，不肯说的真言，说些与大众听一听&rdquo;，</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">103</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">&ldquo;眼见一切经典，三教文字，真言秘诀，心得开悟，便当礼拜赞叹&rdquo;。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">104</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《龙门心法》里三教并提的现象，正是明清时期三教合一思潮越来越盛行的反映。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">综上所述，王常月的修道思想可概括为持戒入定生慧而降伏身心意。而其中的关键又是&ldquo;以戒摄心&rdquo;。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">105</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">也就是说，王常月所谓的修道，其实是以修心为主。他说：&ldquo;修道全凭一点心，心真念切道为邻。&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">106</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">这样一种思想，在道教中也是有着悠久的历史的。大约出于隋唐之际的《太上老君内观经》即认为，&ldquo;心者，禁也，一身之主&rdquo;，&ldquo;人能常清静其心，则道自来居&rdquo;，明确提出&ldquo;千经万术，惟在心也&rdquo;，&ldquo;道以心得，心以道明&rdquo;，&ldquo;所以教人修道，则修心也；教人修心，则修道也&rdquo;。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">107</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">注：</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span>1</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">闵一得：《金盖心灯》卷一《王昆阳律师传》，载《藏外道书》，巴蜀书社，1994年版，第31册，第183页。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span>2</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">小柳司气太：《白云观志》，载《中国道观志丛刊》，江苏古籍出版社，2000年版，第1册，第185页。本文所标小柳司气太《白云观志》的页码，均系该书的原页码。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span>3</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《初真戒》收入《道藏辑要》张集七，亦见《藏外道书》第12册影印重刊《道藏辑要》本。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span>4</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《龙门心法》载《藏外道书》第6册，《碧苑坛经》载《藏外道书》第10册。《碧苑坛经》系闵一得在《龙门心法》的基础上&ldquo;订正&rdquo;而成。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span>5</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《初真戒》之《昆阳律师付嘱偈》，《藏外道书》第12册，第30页。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span>6</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">饶宗颐：《老子想尔注校证》，上海古籍出版社，1991年版，第16页。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span>7</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《道藏》，文物出版社、上海书店、天津古籍出版社，1988年版，第18册，第201页。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span>8</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《道藏》第3册，第396页。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span>9</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《太上老君经律》，《道藏》第18册，第219页。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span>10</span><span>12</span><span>17</span><span>19</span><span>20</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">105</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《龙门心法》卷上《戒行精严》，《藏外道书》第6册，第735-738页。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span>11</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《初真戒律&middot;行持总说》，《藏外道书》第12册，第18-19页。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span>13</span><span>18</span><span>70</span><span>89</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">106</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《龙门心法》卷下《印证效验》，《藏外道书》第6册，第764-768页。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span>14</span><span>16</span><span>53</span><span>54</span><span>98</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《龙门心法》卷上《定慧等持》，《藏外道书》第6册，第750-753页。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span>15</span><span>34</span><span>51</span><span>68</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">101</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《龙门心法》卷上《参悟玄微》，《藏外道书》第6册，第744-747页。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span>21</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">王重阳说：&ldquo;今之人欲永不死而离凡世者，大愚不达道理也。&rdquo;（《重阳立教十五论》）&ldquo;是这真性不乱，万缘不挂，无去无来，此是长生不死也。&rdquo;（《重阳真人授丹阳二十四诀》）</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span>22</span><span>23</span><span>26</span><span>31</span><span>37</span><span>47</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《龙门心法》卷上《密行修真》，《藏外道书》第6册，第753-756页。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span>24</span><span>25</span><span>28</span><span>29</span><span>93</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">103</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《龙门心法》卷下《阐教弘道》，《藏外道书》第6册，第770-775页。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span>27</span><span>36</span><span>81</span><span>82</span><span>83</span><span>84</span><span>85</span><span>86</span><span>87</span><span>88</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《龙门心法》卷下《报恩消灾》，《藏外道书》第6册，第758-761页。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span>30</span><span>50</span><span>52</span><span>56</span><span>58</span><span>59</span><span>60</span><span>61</span><span>62</span><span>63</span><span>64</span><span>65</span><span>66</span><span>67</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">100</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《龙门心法》卷上《清净身心》，《藏外道书》第6册，第741-744页。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span>32</span><span>48</span><span>94</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 9pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">102</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《龙门心法》卷下《保命延生》，《藏外道书》第6册，第768-777页。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt" class="p0"><span>33</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">《龙门心法》卷下《功德圆满》，《藏外道书》第6册，第782-785页。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
